    "122105626": {
      "title": "Supersymmetrical String Theories",
      "abstract": "A supersymmetrical light-cone-gauge string action is presented. It provides a basis for understanding the previously-studied supersymmetrical dual string theory as well as two new closed-string theories that have extended supersymmetry in ten dimensions, corresponding to N = 8 supersymmetry in four dimensions."
